{"tid":1295873,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[IOS/AN]足球小將翼Dream Team(25)香港有玩家見面會呀！","createTime":"2019-07-08T07:20:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T07:31:43.000Z","uid":226977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8aee31fa15138738c25257daca153437f1106e5b","tid":1295873,"uid":226977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T07:20:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/15/151526_99f93e79e712ebbe68f16a96e6d75dbf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F15%2F151526_99f93e79e712ebbe68f16a96e6d75dbf.png&h=c5da39e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">足球小將翼Dream Team</span><br />\n問問題前請註明日版/國際版方便巴打解答<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Q&amp;A</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">系統/關卡/任務篇</span><br />\nQ: 點刷首抽<br />\nA: 跟佢步驟會去到0石抽野畫面，抽完唔岩心水可以揀黃色重抽，至小抽到SSR<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/13/131729_ae43fd478018d0987e5a6dfecd48003d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F13%2F131729_ae43fd478018d0987e5a6dfecd48003d.jpg&h=eeebbcf6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以上視為假首抽<br />\n真首抽可以係用佢派嘅石單抽幾次，或者儲夠50石十連<br />\n假首list<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/16/171236_bba1673613bb3e18557478c8f6660011.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F16%2F171236_bba1673613bb3e18557478c8f6660011.jpg&h=d082523c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nQ: 第三個點樣拎？<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/13/154842_f832938bfb178c94a1a3bc7d694820a8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F13%2F154842_f832938bfb178c94a1a3bc7d694820a8.jpg&h=d0d80e69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nA: 一位球員帽子戲法<br />\n<br />\nQ: 唔識分手動，自動，半自動<br />\nA:<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/14/092331_12cd857d20e1b997cf26a5045c91f2f5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F14%2F092331_12cd857d20e1b997cf26a5045c91f2f5.jpg&h=b4e7acde&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nQ: 點解有石都唔比抽<br />\nA: 因為佢有分夢球(有償)同夢球(無償)，分別就係課金石同免費石<br />\n<br />\nQ: 肥料關幾時有？<br />\nA: 公告有交待時間<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/05/104103_cecf5fe66bafba1aa7bf9da7d697bcf1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F05%2F104103_cecf5fe66bafba1aa7bf9da7d697bcf1.jpg&h=70a356eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nQ: 連㩗個任務點解？<br />\nA: 去game setting，揀連㩗<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/21/153441_e1905e834fddf204257c7ece65f0c6fd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F21%2F153441_e1905e834fddf204257c7ece65f0c6fd.jpg&h=080b6370&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n是但㩒一個綠色嘅連㩗左佢 (等同綁定ac）<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/21/153447_400d8f4db4fd09dda526270bbc69d631.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F21%2F153447_400d8f4db4fd09dda526270bbc69d631.jpg&h=5cd82441&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nQ: 係關卡見到挑戰狀xxx又入唔到去<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/19/164807_dacbfec7b7637eb51bec1d5af683dcf9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F19%2F164807_dacbfec7b7637eb51bec1d5af683dcf9.jpg&h=d662cfec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nA: 呢個挑戰狀係課金買的。 手持挑戰狀可以share比盟友一齊打，半場就完，獎金獎品非常豐富！<br />\n<br />\nQ: 點樣轉波衫？<br />\nA: 較陣容個度有個波衫圖案，可以set主場作客同龍門衫。<br />\n<br />\nQ: 每日任務見到有個可以拎1石，但又唔知點做<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/29/173335_8a347067fb01b031444986cab93d3a5b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F29%2F173335_8a347067fb01b031444986cab93d3a5b.jpg&h=bb1543ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nA: 佢意思係完成下面個幾項任務，就會拎到。通常係打紅劵，打故事同友情抽個d。唔識做可以禁隔離個&ldquo;挑戰&ldquo;帶過去<br />\n<br />\n日文翻譯<br />\n轉自巴哈<br />\n球員<br />\nスタミナ Stamina （體力，出技用）<br />\nオフェンス Offence （攻擊）<br />\nドリブル Dribble（盤球）<br />\nシュート Shoot （射球）<br />\nパス Pass （傳送）<br />\nディフェンス Defense （防守）<br />\nタックル Tackle （搶截）<br />\nブロック Block （封阻）<br />\nパスカット Cut pass （攔截傳球）<br />\nフィジカル Physical （體能）<br />\nスピード Speed （速度）<br />\nパワー Power （力量）<br />\nテクニック Technique （技術）<br />\n守門員<br />\nセービング Saving （撲救）<br />\nパンチ Punch（手鎚）<br />\nキャッチ Catch（接實）"},{"pid":"aca2ad993b12bc15b4b1e59520c8b7e7a4f2d178","tid":1295873,"uid":226977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T07:24:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">卡片/角色/技能篇</span><br />\nQ: 開局抽乜最好<br />\nA: 限威限三<br />\n<img src=\"https://truth.bahamut.com.tw/s01/201903/cec6cd71234071251d355bf69ecd630d.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftruth.bahamut.com.tw%2Fs01%2F201903%2Fcec6cd71234071251d355bf69ecd630d.JPG&h=b4f7b2a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://truth.bahamut.com.tw/s01/201902/9262fd30484d3006a3336892c9fd8ca0.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftruth.bahamut.com.tw%2Fs01%2F201902%2F9262fd30484d3006a3336892c9fd8ca0.JPG&h=8e3a2e02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外可以自己參考下<br />\n【心得】各球員推薦與評論2.0版<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=31996&amp;snA=2851&amp;tnum=54&amp;subbsn=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D31996%26snA%3D2851%26tnum%3D54%26subbsn%3D3&d=JetPiwFZRsNB2TajAgP4V0n12mAFq1syGW6OSBl8LUM%3D&h=5b9fdd44\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=31996&amp;snA=2851&amp;tnum=54&amp;subbsn=3</a><br />\n總之月尾/特別大活動先好開局，或者淘個ACC無咁嬲<br />\n<br />\nQ: 限定係咩黎?<br />\nA: 限定有分兩種<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/27/113825_f932477cd33e4a26a4d9128e591fc382.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F27%2F113825_f932477cd33e4a26a4d9128e591fc382.jpg&h=81de7aa9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/27/113829_67139574ed69b627df04b210ecd559ad.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F27%2F113829_67139574ed69b627df04b210ecd559ad.jpg&h=d046fd04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n留意番上圖係月尾限, 下圖係月中限(日文字唔同的, 而且月尾限角色有自己大頭係背景)<br />\n主力留石抽月尾限, 月中限適合重課/有愛人士<br />\n<br />\nQ: 勞比杜 賀茂 吉良 見上有乜用<br />\nA: 前面三位都係加額外數值 見上用黎升龍門(類似pad蛋龍)<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/14/152230_40826eff5026bca7a354e338a3c94cdb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F14%2F152230_40826eff5026bca7a354e338a3c94cdb.jpg&h=4016f3d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n至於點睇球員加幾多係max<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/17/111034_0c2acf26c1b8f5a95ffacd6d6a4eb41c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F17%2F111034_0c2acf26c1b8f5a95ffacd6d6a4eb41c.jpg&h=be6955a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nQ: 咩係覺醒？<br />\nA: 簡單黎講SSR&gt;UR，SR&gt;SSR，只可覺醒一次<br />\n<br />\nQ: 咩係能力上限突破<br />\nA: 當UR升滿lv，教練後，可以突破原有能力<br />\n有100點可以分配（龍門75），每項能力最多加25點<br />\n則係能力加1000<br />\n即是可以分配最小4項能力去到上限<br />\n素材就曜日關打，分屬性，日本定海外<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/15/162635_326a9c8dd83730052b10747bd3b7d287.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F15%2F162635_326a9c8dd83730052b10747bd3b7d287.png&h=f3d15264&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【攻略】「能力極限突破」特效球員<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=31996&amp;snA=2888&amp;tnum=3&amp;subbsn=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D31996%26snA%3D2888%26tnum%3D3%26subbsn%3D3&d=JetPiwFZRsNB2TajAgP4V0n12mAFq1syGW6OSBl8LUM%3D&h=80a25ab0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=31996&amp;snA=2888&amp;tnum=3&amp;subbsn=3</a><br />\n<br />\nQ: 點樣快速賺150金幣換ssr劵？<br />\nA：唔好就咁賣走抽番黎既sr卡，將佢地升滿lv再覺醒，賣／食左去就有15金一隻（原本1金），做10次等交換所更新見到有得換就可以換到1張 （total有2張）。順便一提賣／食ur有30金。<br />\n<br />\nQ: 咩係潛能覺醒<br />\nA: 將球員ge能力再進一步提升，但暫時唔係所有球員可以<br />\n【其他】潛能覺醒球員名單<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=31996&amp;snA=2969\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D31996%26snA%3D2969&d=JetPiwFZRsNB2TajAgP4V0n12mAFq1syGW6OSBl8LUM%3D&h=dcbe72c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=31996&amp;snA=2969</a><br />\n【攻略】「潛能覺醒」重點攻略<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=31996&amp;snA=2891\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D31996%26snA%3D2891&d=JetPiwFZRsNB2TajAgP4V0n12mAFq1syGW6OSBl8LUM%3D&h=67bc771f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=31996&amp;snA=2891</a><br />\n<br />\nQ: 見到志偉泰萊個d識出雙人技，有咩條件？<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/05/133311_8f10bd21f3143ff67bb9adb277a76808.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F05%2F133311_8f10bd21f3143ff67bb9adb277a76808.jpg&h=096414f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nA：長按睇球員技能個陣，有d會有兩個公仔就代表要個個人同場先出得（再長按招技可以睇到要咩人同場）。扣體力只扣出技個個，同場個位唔會扣。 <br />\n<br />\nQ: 咁招技寫住sp又代表咩？<br />\nA: SP代表招技有特殊效果，都係長按招技就睇到。通常都係3款：吹飛，角度無視，距離無視<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">連盟篇</span><br />\nQ: 咩係連盟？有咩用<br />\nA: 連盟功能個人7lv開放，功能如下<br />\n-同連盟嘅兄弟一齊完成任務，賺綠幣，射六格，獎品豐富<br />\n-捐錢比球會，提升回報或加球員數值<br />\n-開場同連盟兄弟一齊打關，一人體力四人回報<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/16/175821_fd15181d2c9ad91bf5659e3abfa79ddb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F16%2F175821_fd15181d2c9ad91bf5659e3abfa79ddb.jpg&h=1b0ddda8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n－請善用連盟內置聊天版同盟友聯絡<br />\n－退盟要冷卻24小時先可以轉會<br />\n<br />\n任何問題請多多發問，頭post未必能緊貼最新資訊"},{"pid":"53f64087a3e6ccdd90cf392153391245d50846d2","tid":1295873,"uid":226977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T07:31:43.000Z","msg":"嘩！8月4日 足球小將Dream Team香港有見面會呀！開發團隊也會與玩家們見面交流，又會解答各位玩家的問題。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/tsubasaDTtc/posts/2237538516561274?__tn__=-R-R\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FtsubasaDTtc%2Fposts%2F2237538516561274%3F__tn__%3D-R-R&d=JetPiwFZRsNB2TajAgP4V0n12mAFq1syGW6OSBl8LUM%3D&h=13cfe97f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/tsubasaDTtc/posts/2237538516561274?__tn__=-R-R</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/07/08/GWH1J4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F07%2F08%2FGWH1J4.jpg&h=417a11f5&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}